layout.css: flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; flex: 0 0 auto; width: 16rem;

layout.format: To add/remove/rename pages, select the "sidebar" tab at the bottom and adjust the configuration.
To edit the contents of a page, click on elements and edit/add/delete them as required. To adjust the settings of an element, select it and edit properties it in the bottom toolbox.
To attach UI control to your device, add REST API endpoint first, then select a control and set the 'API variable' to that endpoint.
To edit the configuration manually, click on the "export" button to download wizard.json configuration file. Edit it, and import back.
Click on the "Docs" toolbar button to view the JSON format details.
